text: Kızkalesi means "Maiden's castle" in Turkish and iy may refer to; *Kızkalesi (ancient Corycus) a town in Erdemli district of Mersin Province *Kızkalesi a castle built on a small islet and facing the town Kızkalesi ==See also== *Kızlar Kalesi *Kızlar Monastery *Kız Kulesi
